snippet.title: Hello Neighbor 3 - Prototype 1 | Full Game Walkthrough
snippet.description:
The first Prototype of Hello Neighbor 3 is out now. It is not at all close to what the full game will be like. But in Prototype 1, we get introduced to the atmosphere and characters AI for the first time. Although the Neighbor and the Guest are not present in this build, they will be part of the full game. In this build we have to complete a set of puzzles to get out of the town and I hope you will like this Full Game Walkthrough of Hello Neighbor Prototype 1.

One of the focus of Hello Neighbor 3 is live events happening in a half abandoned town. I have tried to capture such live evets happening with the characters in Prototype 1 and I hope you will enjoy watching this video :)

Hello Neighbor 3 description - A cozy yet eerie adventure, where every path is the right one, and every action leads to discovery. Explore and influence Raven Brooks, a half-abandoned town simulated in real-time.

THANKS FOR WATCHING!!!
